Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.89,0:01:30.06,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}闇の楽園は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.89,0:01:30.06,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}暗夜的樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.38,0:01:31.80,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嘘か夢か
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.38,0:01:31.80,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是夢是幻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.17,0:01:33.80,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}失うのは身体と
