Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.17,0:01:33.80,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}失去的是身體
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.87,0:01:35.37,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}自分という心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.87,0:01:35.37,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}和自我之心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.46,0:01:37.16,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その対価を差し出し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.46,0:01:37.16,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}付出如此代價
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:40.23,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}何を得られるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:40.23,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}又能得到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:43.99,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}この涙で奪える程に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:43.99,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}連這淚水都能將之奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:47.31,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}命は脆くて儚くて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:47.31,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}生命脆弱而飄忽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:50.78,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}全てに訪れる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:50.78,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}當一切造訪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:54.11,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}死を「恐怖」と嘆くのか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:54.11,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs14\pos(235,330)}終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:54.11,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要將死亡歎作恐怖嗎
