Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:02:01.10,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}靜靜綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:02.78,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}憎しみも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:02.78,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}將憎恨
