Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:08.06,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その根でたくり寄せて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:08.06,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}全部寄於根莖
